The paper proposes an unsupervised approach for discovering relevant tutorial fragments for APIs, which involves natural language processing techniques such as pronoun resolution and topic modeling. This suggests that the paper may belong to the Information Retrieval (cs.IR), Software Engineering (cs.SE), Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), Machine Learning (cs.LG), or Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories.
